                <td>HTTP/OAuth</td>
                <td><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoftteams/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">learn.microsoft.com</a></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <div class="callout">
            <strong>OAuth:</strong> This plugin uses OAuth. The MCP server will open
            a browser window for authentication when you first connect.
          </div>
          <h4>MCP Config</h4>
          <pre><code>{`{
  "servers": {
    "Microsoft Teams": {
      "type": "http",
      "url": "https://agent365.svc.cloud.microsoft/agents/tenants/\${input:tenant_id}/servers/mcp_TeamsServer"
    }
  }
}`}</code></pre>
          <div class="callout">
            <strong>Note:</strong> Replace <code>$&#123;input:tenant_id&#125;</code> with your
            Microsoft 365 tenant ID. In VS Code, this will prompt you for the value
            when the server starts.
          </div>
        </section>
